GateDocument.TextWithNodes: WORKSHOP ON DATABASE THEORY ( Last minute call for papers ) Submissions are invited for a workshop on theoretical aspects of databases to be held during the second week of ESSLLI'97 , ( 18 - 22 August ) . Possible topics include , but are not limited to , - database schema design - dependencies - constraints - representing incomplete / imprecise information - dynamic aspects of databases - applications of finite model theory / complexity theory . Please send short abstracts by email to the workshop organiser , Natasha Alechina ( N . Alechina @ jw . dj . sucb ) before 25 June . - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
